data.description: This Home is Pristine and Move In Ready! Light and Bright with Modern Colors and Beautiful Windows. The Open Concept Kitchen and Great Room Feature Laminate Flooring Throughout, A Gas Fireplace, Charming Kitchen with Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, and Large Walk In Pantry. A Glass Patio Door Leads you to the Wonderfully Landscaped Backyard and Patio, w/Territorial Views. The Large Master Suite has A Soak Tub, Walk In Shower, Double Sinks And a Handsome Walk in Closet. Features Upper Laundry Room, Two Additional Spacious Bedrooms, A full Bath, Den/Home Office Room. Great Location with Restaurants and Shopping. The Seller is offering a Closing Cost Credit for a Rate Buy Down with an Acceptable offer.
